測資本市場的未來變化趨勢，使每一筆投資都能取得相當可觀的收益。目前&ldquo;禪易投資法&rdquo;已經獲得中國及美國國家版權局授予的多項著作權。<br />\n<br />\n厲害了 我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T08:19:13.000Z","msg":"同沈大師有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:25:11.000Z","msg":"沈大師如果推遲2 3年其實好撚準"},{"pid":"f46455cfa10aa7b14e15faf006c4e959b1d93964","tid":1786505,"uid":37524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"397f987eb10a4f370f1ffe9178de06c2233e8c9e","tid":1786505,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T08:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廢老咪搞事 有得食比你著仲想點 停牌有咩問題 出綠狗拉你呀喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:34:02.000Z","msg":"你啱<br />\n今日咁得閒出嚟集會多數係藍絲廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94e49974ca6d97baa1890a6db17d7675aed9ee0","tid":1786505,"uid":21398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2537c488c71b3e0840894bf5676a1f18a1899f65","tid":1786505,"uid":62871,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T07:57:15.000Z","msg":"好撚明顯係公司有事先會停。咁撚豬買埋呢d股票，抵畀人呃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:35:46.000Z","msg":"唔停牌，跌到渣都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0901aaad420ed5da41325330707fcd86441cb8f0","tid":1786505,"uid":36378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:38:46.000Z","msg":"呢d垃圾真係傻西先會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afef5f8c3a1c8fe41f9c9e753b5e1e794d4edd0f","tid":1786505,"uid":102078,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:44:23.